headline: MTCH Bronstein, Gewirtz & Grossman LLC Announces that Match Group, Inc. Investors with Substantial Losses Have Opportunity to Lead Class Action Lawsuit
summary: NEW YORK, Nov. 28, 2024 /PRNewswire/ -- Attorney Advertising -- Bronstein, Gewirtz & Grossman, LLC, a nationally recognized law firm, notifies investors that a class action lawsuit has been filed...
